<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink340">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi kātala</l>
<l>ruḷḷār koṉṉā maruḷuṟ ṟaṉaṅkol</l>
<l>viṭṭuc ceṉṟaṉar nammē</l>
<l>taṭṭait tīyi ṉūrala reḻavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>Does the lover even think of us? Or are we merely deluded? </l>
<l>He left us and went away, setting rumors ablaze in the village, </l>
<l>[spreading] like fire through a bamboo [grove]. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
